plaster.en-uk:
an adhesive bandage placed on a minor cut or scrape (UK also: sticking/sticky 
plaster, Elastoplast; US: Band-Aid);
a cast of plaster of Paris ("a leg in plaster")

tart.en-uk:
female prostitute
